        This website is generated with Cobalt, a static website generator written in Rust.
        It uses liquid templates and markdown to generate HTML pages.
      </p>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <!-- Project link 3 -->
    <div class="page-text-block clearfix">
      <a href="/projects/sintel">
        <div class="thumbnail">
          <img src="../assets/sintel_logo.png" alt"image"/>
        </div>
        <h4>Sintel</h4>
      </a>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.2em; color: #767676">Technologie used Rust, Dyon</p>
      <p>
        Sintel is a a 2D game engine and is not a general purpose engine.
        This engine is build for building 2d isometric games.
        Sintel is written in Rust, a safe system programming language.
        Sintel is a collection of seperate libraries that make up the game engine.
      </p>
    </div>
    <hr>
  </div>
</main>
